Class BasicTestCase

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BasicPutAndGetTestCase, BoundedShapeExtendsLocatableTestCase, BoundedShapeInheritanceTestCase, BoundedShapePropertiesTestCase, BoundedShapeTagTestCase, CmdIntEditablePropTestCase, CmdIntTagTestCase, ConsoleViewConstructorAddListenerTestCase, ConsoleViewConstructorParameterTestCase, ConsoleViewListenerTestCase, ConsoleViewTagTestCase, EncapsulationTestCase, ErrorTestCase, EventTracerTestCase, FailingTestCase, GetInvalidTestCase, GetNullTestCase, InterfaceTypeTestCase, ListenerCollectionTestCase, LocatableInheritanceTestCase, LocatablePropertiesTestCase, LocatableTagTestCase, MainClassTestCase, ManualTestCase, PassingTestCase, PutExistingTestCase, PutNullTestCase, QuestionTestCase, SettersNotifyTestCase, ShapesRegisterListenerTestCase, SingleInterfaceTestCase, SystemExitTestCase, TableTagTestCase, TaggedMethodTestCase, TestCaseWrapper, ThreePackageTestCase

    public abstract class BasicTestCase
extends Object
implements TestCase
    All test cases should extend this class. Subclasses will implement the TestCase.test(framework.project.Project, boolean) method. This method should call and return one of the following helper functions:
    • pass()
    • pass(String)
    • partialPass(double)
    • partialPass(double, String)
    • fail(String)
    An example: 
     return partialPass(0.5, "Only got half of the points");
